" Vim Script To Configure Simple Vim Settings

syntax enable
set autoindent
filetype indent plugin on
set nostartofline
set confirm
set mouse=a
set hidden
set tabstop=4
set softtabstop=4
set expandtab
set number
set title
set showcmd
set cursorline
set wildmenu
set showmatch
set visualbell
set hls " highlight results in search
set ic " ignore capitialization on letters in searches
set is " show partial matches
